{'name': 'RealEstateAPI.get_financial_report', 'description': 'This function retrieves the financial report of a real estate developer based on the developer name and report type.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'developerName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the real estate developer.'}, {'name': 'reportType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of report to retrieve, e.g., latest, quarterly, annual.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'financialReport', 'description': 'The financial report of the developer.'}]}

想法: 你这一步的目标

动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 RealEstateAPI.get_financial_report, 它的参数输入如下: 'developerName'是'GreenBuild Developers', 'reportType'是'latest'.
